      "description": "A nice opportunity to get into an honest driver at a reasonable price. This car is in fair condition overall, with the kind of age and wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, but it still presents well enough to enjoy as-is while you improve it over time. A good fit for someone who wants a solid, affordable car without paying top-tier money.",
