    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid good-condition example that appears complete, presentable, and ready to enjoy as a driver. It shows well overall with decent paint, trim, and interior, and it comes across as a car that has been kept up better than the average older driver. Expect a clean, usable classic rather than a fully restored or show-level vehicle, so there may still be some minor age-related cosmetic flaws and wear in places. Overall, this looks like an honest, above-average car for someone who wants something nice to use and improve gradually if desired.",
