      "description": "Poor-condition vehicle being sold honestly as a project or fixer-upper. It shows significant cosmetic wear inside and out, with aged paint, visible imperfections, and a tired overall presentation. Expect mechanical needs, deferred maintenance, and repairs before it can be considered dependable for regular use. Best suited for a buyer looking for a restoration candidate, parts car, or budget project rather than a turn-key driver.",
