    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age and will appeal best to someone looking for a low-cost daily driver, project, or dependable backup car. Priced to move and represented honestly, it offers an accessible entry point for anyone who prioritizes budget over cosmetics. A practical opportunity to own for less.",
